<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a href="/wiki/File:SITARAMDAS_OMKARNATH.jpg" class="image"><img alt="SITARAMDAS OMKARNATH.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/16/SITARAMDAS_OMKARNATH.jpg/220px-SITARAMDAS_OMKARNATH.jpg" width="220" height="317" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/16/SITARAMDAS_OMKARNATH.jpg/330px-SITARAMDAS_OMKARNATH.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/16/SITARAMDAS_OMKARNATH.jpg/440px-SITARAMDAS_OMKARNATH.jpg 2x" data-file-width="510" data-file-height="736" /></a></td>
