<tr>
<th scope="row">Born</th>
<td>Probodh Chandra Chattopadhya<br />
<span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1892-02-17</span>)</span>17 February 1892<br />
Keota Village, <a href="/wiki/Hooghly_district" title="Hooghly district">Hooghly district</a>, <a href="/wiki/West_Bengal" title="West Bengal">West Bengal</a>, <a href="/wiki/India" title="India">India</a><sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Died</th>
<td>6 December 1982<span style="display:none">(<span class="dday deathdate">1982-12-06</span>)</span> (aged&#160;90)<br />
India</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Guru</th>
<td>Dasarathidev Yogeswar of Digsui Village</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Philosophy</th>
<td><a href="/wiki/Sanathana_Darma" title="Sanathana Darma" class="mw-redirect">Sanathana Darma</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Quotation</th>
<td>Faith in the divine Name is not blind faith. Call Him howsoever you will, call Him, standing, sitting, eating, going to bed - peace shall be yours.<sup id="cite_ref-Cloudburst_2-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Cloudburst-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup><sup class="reference" style="white-space:nowrap;">(c.2¶.77)</sup></td>
</tr>
